, and research equipment industries. The company was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in Hayward, California.", "fullTimeEmployees": 6948, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Jinsong  Xiao", "age": 54, "title": "CEO & Director", "yearBorn": 1971, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 990976, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Sheri L. Savage", "age": 54, "title": "Chief Financial Officer & Senior VP of Finance", "yearBorn": 1971, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 1102431, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Jeffrey L. Mckibben", "age": 62, "title": "Chief Information Officer", "yearBorn": 1963, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 769076, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Christopher S. Cook", "age": 56, "title": "Chief Business Officer", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 940483, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Robert  Wunar", "title": "Chief Operating Officer", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Brian E. Harding CPA", "age": 44, "title": "Senior VP & Chief Accounting Officer", "yearBorn": 1981, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Rhonda M. Bennetto B.B.A.", "title": "Senior Vice President of Investor Relations", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Yoonku  Cho", "age": 47, "title": "General Counsel & Corporate Secretary", "yearBorn": 1978, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Cheryl  Knepfler", "title": "Managing Director of Marketing", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Jamie J. Palfrey", "age": 57, "title": "Chief Human Resources Officer", "yearBorn": 1968, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}], "aud